short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Re-order amazon orders by delivery date.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Also arrange in a grid, and load multiple pages at once.

Shows your tabs in a grid on the new tab page. Includes thumbnails of each tab and keyboard shortcuts for saving tabs.

File bug reports here: https://github.com/sliftist/az-order/issues

Contribute  to the extension here: https://github.com/sliftist/az-order/
